es and most importantly in our investigations Director Mueller has said In speaking about the FBI he stated We have the best investigators in the world in this institution and some of the best people here at headquarters that carry me The challenge is to get them the tools that they need to become even better And that is what we are working on The joy of it is that you are doing it for the country you are doing it for other FBI agents you are doing it for the community and you are doing it for the people That is tremendously rewarding hq htm Headquarters and Programs Learn more about FBI divisions investigative areas and the organizational chart libref executives asstmain htm FBI libref executives asstmain htm Executives Leadership at FBI Headquarters contact fo fo htm Field Offices Contact information for an FBI office near you contact legat legat htm Legal Attache Offices Overseas FBI representation aboutus tour tour htm FBI Tour Information Public tours are closed business business htm Business Opportunities Information about contract opportunities with the FBI libref historic fbiseal fbiseal htm Heraldry of the Seal Each symbol and color in the FBI seal has special significance aboutus faqs faqsone htm Frequently Asked Questions Learn more about us in the frequently asked questions section
